<i>noun</i>: 숙소 [숙쏘], 숙박업소 [숙빠겁쏘] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>숙소 [숙쏘]</dt><br>
<dd>lodging; accommodations</dd><br>
<dd>집이 아닌 임시로 머물러 묵는 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>A place that is not one's house where one stays temporarily,</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>숙박업소 [숙빠겁쏘]</dt><br>
<dd>accommodations; lodgings</dd><br>
<dd>여관이나 호텔 등과 같이 요금을 받고 손님을 숙박시키는 영업을 하는 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>A place of business that receives payment for accommodating guests, such as an inn, hotel, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>